<h2>Missions</h2>

<p>ValidFi's mission is to provide <span style="font:bold" class="orange">holistic, systematic, comprehensive and actionable</span> strategies for financial planning and investment. The holistic approach means ValidFi starts from the overall financial and investment portfolio planning and moves down to individual strategies. The systematic approach means ValidFi's strategies are consistent, precise and step by step. ValidFi collects many financial strategies found in magazines, books, academic papers and those proposed by users. Finally, the strategies provided are actionable and can be readily used in practice. We specialize in <span class="orange"><bl>HOW</bl></span>, not just <span class="orange"><bl>WHAT.</bl><span></p>

<h2>Overview</h2>

<p>ValidFi's approach ceters around quantitative strategies. The strategy center collects many strategies ranging from financial planning to asset allocation to asset investment. These strategies form a rich knowledge base for users to study, apply or merely use as references. The portfolio center provides actionable portfolios based on (multiple) strategies. Model portfolios are supplied to showcase how to construct and monitor a portfolio. The tool center provides a quantitative platform for portfolio simulation and analysis, asset allocation and financial planning (forthcoming). The fund center provides real time asset allocation for mutual funds and ETFs. Furthermore, mutual fund trading styles could be analyzed based on the funds' underlying a behavior or strategy employed.</p>

