<h2>Tool Center</h2>

<ul>
<li><h3>Platform</h3>
<p>ValidFi offers an institutional quality platform for planning and investment strategies and portfolio management. Its salient features include:</p>
   <ul>
   <li> Structured Portfolio Construction: asset allocation, strategies and portfolios are first class citizens.</li>
   <li> Programmable Strategies.</li>   
   <li> Local execution: simulating a portfolio could be carried out in local machines to allow support of proprietary data and APIs. This reduces the slowdown for our central servers too.</li>
   <li> Historical simulation of portfolios: back testing based on historical data for a portfolio with (multiple) strategies.</li>
   <li>Portfolio statistics: Analytics of portfolios include MPT (Modern Portfolio Theory) statistics: The very basic goal of investment is to achieve good returns with reasonable risk. Popular statistics such as annualized returns, IRR (Internal Rate of Return), alpha, beta, standard deviation, Sharpe and maximum drawdown for various periods are computed.</li>
   <li>Powerful charting: The portfolio transaction log, other messages and the statistics are viewed through annotated charts.</li>
   <li>Live monitoring of portfolios including trading signals: Portfolios could be setup as 'LIVE' and ValidFi will automatically update the portfolios based on the current markets.</li>
   <li>Hierarchical Portfolio Construction: ValidFi offers a powerful and natural way to allow a portfolio to be hierarchically constructed. An example is the Simple Core Satellite Portfolio strategy. This portfolio consists of two other portfolios and they in term are made of other portfolios. Multiple strategies could be developed and evaluated using this feature. Diversification not only comes as multiple asset class investment, but also as multiple strategies on those asset classes or even in the overall portfolio asset/strategy allocation.</li>
   <li>Statistical significance testing for investment strategies: confidence level testing is provided for rigorous study of the effectiveness of strategies.</li>
   <li>Up to date latest news and discussion feeds: ValidFi will automatically search well qualified web sources on any update, newly published books and papers on individual strategies.</li>
   </ul>
</li>
